          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2098.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, trim your<strong> asparagus</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>asparagus tips</strong> away from the stalks and set them aside</p><p>Roughly chop the <strong>asparagus stalks</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2098.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2098.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2098.-step-5-x700.jpg",
