          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2098.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2098.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the rice is almost cooked, add the<strong> asparagus tips </strong>to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 5-6 min or until bright green and tender with a bite – these are your<strong> roasted asparagus tips</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
