    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped asparagus stalks</strong> to the pan and cook for 5 min further until the rice is cooked and the asparagus is tender</p><p>Add the juice of half your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> and your<strong> grated cheese</strong> and give everything a good mix up until fully combined</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>asparagus risotto</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
